ed websites."},{"question":"Can you improve my website speed during redesigning?","answer":"Yes, website redesign includes performance improvements such as optimizing images, improving code structure, reducing unnecessary elements, and enhancing overall loading speed."}] -->', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1498050108023-c5249f4df085?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80', 'website', '2026-05-27 06:21:09', '2026-06-20 05:19:54', 1, 'Revamp Your Business Website with Expert Website Redesign Services in Ranchi, Jharkhand', 'Upgrade your online presence with professional Website Redesign Services in Ranchi, Jharkhand. Global Webify transforms outdated websites into modern, fast, and SEO-friendly designs that improve user experience and boost business growth.', 'image', '#062013', '#062013', '#0c3e25', NULL, NULL),
