></p></li><li><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Audience Research &amp; Targeting</span></p></li><li><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Conversion Tracking Setup</span></p></li><li><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Campaign Monitoring &amp; Performance Optimization</span></p></li><li><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Monthly Reporting &amp; Analytics</span></p></li></ul><h3><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Our Step-by-Step Facebook Marketing Process</strong></span></h3><h4><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>1. Business &amp; Audience Analysis</strong></span></h4><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">We understand your business goals, industry, competitors, and target customers to build a solid marketing foundation.</span></p><h4><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>2. Strategy Development</strong></span></h4><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Our experts create a customized Facebook marketing strategy focused on achieving your specific objectives.</span></p><h4><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>3. Campaign Setup</strong></span></h4><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">We configure campaigns, audience targeting, ad placements, tracking systems, and budget allocations.</span></p><h4><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>4. Creative Development</strong></span></h4><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Our team designs engaging visuals and compelling ad copy that encourage user interaction and conversions.</span></p><h4><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>5. Campaign Launch &amp; Optimization</strong></span></h4><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Once campaigns go live, we continuously monitor performance and make strategic improvements.</span></p><h4><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>6. Reporting &amp; Growth Planning</strong></span></h4><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Detailed reports help identify opportunities for scaling successful campaigns and improving future performance.</span></p