(91117, '/crm-software-development', 'CRM Software Development Company in Ranchi', 'CRM Software Development Company in Ranchi, Custom CRM Software Services in Ranchi', 'Global Webify is a leading CRM Software Development Company in Ranchi offering Custom CRM Software Services in Ranchi, Jharkhand. Boost your business, contact us today!', 'CRM Software Development Company in Ranchi, Custom CRM Software Services in Ranchi, CRM Development in Ranchi, CRM Solutions in Jharkhand, Business CRM Software in Jharkhand, Custom Software Development Jharkhand', '<p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Efficient customer relationship management is essential for organizations aiming to improve customer engagement, increase conversions, and simplify daily operations. A reliable CRM system helps manage leads, track sales activities, automate follow-ups, and maintain valuable customer data in one centralized platform.</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">As a leading <strong>CRM Software Development Company in Ranchi</strong>, Jharkhand, Global Webify delivers customized CRM solutions designed to support business growth, improve workflow efficiency, and strengthen customer relationships. Whether you are a startup, small enterprise, or established organization, a tailored CRM system can help streamline operations and enhance decision-making through real-time data insights.</span></p><h2><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Custom CRM Software Services in Ranchi to Streamline Sales, Leads &amp; Customer Management</strong></span></h2><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Organizations often face challenges such as scattered customer information, missed follow-ups, inefficient communication, and manual data handling. Our <strong>Custom CRM Software Services in Ranchi</strong> are designed to eliminate these challenges by providing a centralized and scalable platform that improves productivity and customer engagement.</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Our custom CRM solutions are built to align with your unique business requirements and operational goals. From lead generation to customer retention, every process can be optimized through automation and intelligent workflows.</span></p><h3><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Benefits of CRM Software: Improve Sales, Service &amp; Productivity</strong></span></h3><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">A well-developed CRM system offers significant advantages across departments and business functions.</span></p><ul><li><p>Centralized customer data management</p></li><li><p>Faster lead tracking and follow-up processes</p></li><li><p>Improved customer communication and engagement</p></li><li><p>Enhanced sales pipeline visibility</p></li><li><p>Automated task and workflow management</p></li><li><p>Better team collaboration and coordination</p></li><li><p>Real-time reporting and business analytics</p></li><li><p>Increased customer retention and satisfaction</p></li><li><p>Reduced manual work and operational errors</p></li><li><p>Higher productivity and revenue growth</p></li></ul><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">With the right CRM platform, organizations can make informed decisions, improve service quality, and build stronger customer relationships.</span></p><h3><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>What Our CRM Development Services Offer You</strong></span></h3><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Our comprehensive CRM development solutions are designed to support businesses across various industries. We focus on creating secure, scalable, and user-friendly systems that deliver measurable results.</span></p><h4><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Our CRM Development Services Include:</strong></span></h4><ul><li><p>Custom CRM Development</p></li><li><p>CRM Software Design &amp; Development</p></li><li><p>Lead Management System Development</p></li><li><p>Sales Automation Solutions</p></li><li><p>Customer Support Management Systems</p></li><li><p>Workflow Automation Integration</p></li><li><p>CRM Dashboard &amp; Reporting Modules</p></li><li><p>Third-Party API Integrations</p></li><li><p>Cloud-Based CRM Solutions</p></li><li><p>Mobile CRM Application Development</p></li><li><p>CRM Migration &amp; Upgradation Services</p></li><li><p>CRM Maintenance &amp; Technical Support</p></li></ul><h4><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Key Features We Develop</strong></span></h4><ul><li><p>Contact and customer database management</p></li><li><p>Lead capture and nurturing tools</p></li><li><p>Sales tracking and opportunity management</p></li><li><p>Task scheduling and reminders</p></li><li><p>Email and communication tracking</p></li><li><p>Customer support ticket management</p></li><li><p>Custom reports and analytics</p></li><li><p>Role-based access controls</p></li><li><p>Marketing automation features</p></li><li><p>Multi-user collaboration tools</p></li></ul><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Every CRM solution is developed with flexibility and scalability in mind, allowing organizations to adapt as their operational needs evolve.</span></p><h3><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Why Choose Us as Your CRM Development Company in Ranchi</strong></span></h3><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Selecting the right development partner is crucial for the success of your CRM implementation. Our team focuses on delivering solutions that are practical, scalable, and aligned with your business objectives.</span></p><h4><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Reasons to Partner With Us</strong></span></h4><ul><li><p>Experienced CRM developers and consultants</p></li><li><p>Fully customized CRM development approach</p></li><li><p>Industry-specific CRM solutions</p></li><li><p>User-friendly and intuitive interfaces</p></li><li><p>Secure and scalable architecture</p></li><li><p>Seamless third-party integrations</p></li><li><p>Agile development methodology</p></li><li><p>Transparent communication throughout the project</p></li><li><p>Dedicated post-launch support</p></li><li><p>Cost-effective development solutions</p></li></ul><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Our development process begins with understanding your business requirements and identifying workflow challenges. We then design and develop a CRM platform that improves operational efficiency, strengthens customer relationships, and supports long-term business growth.</span></p><h3><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Transform Customer Management with a Custom CRM Solution</strong></span></h3><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Managing customer interactions, sales activities, and support operations becomes easier with a CRM system tailored to your business needs. A custom-built CRM platform helps improve team productivity, increase customer satisfaction, and create a structured approach to business growth.</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">From lead management and sales automation to customer service and reporting, our CRM development expertise helps organizations gain better control over their operations while delivering exceptional customer experiences. Partner with Global Webify to build a powerful CRM solution that supports sustainable growth and operational excellence.</span></p>\n<!-- FAQ_DATA: [{"question":"What is CRM Software Development?","answer":"CRM Software Development is the process of creating customized customer relationship management software that helps businesses manage leads, customers, sales processes, communication, and business operations from one centralized platform."},{"question":"Why does my business need custom CRM software?","answer":"Custom CRM software helps businesses automate daily tasks, improve customer relationships, track sales activities, manage leads efficiently, and get better insights through reports and analytics. It is designed according to your specific business requirements."},{"question":"What services does Global Webify provide for CRM Software Development?","answer":"Global Webify provides complete CRM Software Development solutions, including custom CRM development, CRM customization, CRM integration, sales management systems, lead tracking solutions, automation workflows, and ongoing support."},{"question":"Can Global Webify develop CRM software according to my business needs?","answer":"Yes, Global Webify develops customized CRM solutions based on your business workflow, industry requirements, team structure, and operational goals. We create CRM systems that fit your exact requirements instead of providing a one-size-fits-all solution."},{"question":"How can CRM software help increase sales?","answer":"CRM software helps sales teams track every customer interaction, follow up on leads at the right time, automate repetitive tasks, and identify better sales opportunities, which improves conversion rates and customer retention."},{"question":"Is CRM software suitable for small and large businesses?","answer":"Yes, CRM software can be customized for startups, small businesses, and large enterprises. It helps businesses of all sizes organize customer data, improve productivity, and manage growth efficiently."}] -->', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552664730-d307ca884978?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80', 'crm', '2026-06-12 06:38:42', '2026-06-20 05:26:41', 1, 'Ranchi''s Trusted CRM Software Development Company for Smart Businesses', 'As a leading CRM Software Development Company in Ranchi, Jharkhand, we create scalable and customized CRM solutions that help businesses manage leads, automate processes, enhance customer engagement, and drive growth.\n', 'image', '#062013', '#062013', '#0c3e25', NULL, NULL),
(91118, '/lead-management-software', 'Lead Management Software Company in Ranchi', 'Lead Management Software Company in Ranchi, Lead Management System in Ranchi', 'Global Webify, a leading Lead Management Software Company in Ranchi, offers smart Lead Management System in Ranchi to boost sales & growth. Contact us today!', 'Lead Management Software Company in Ranchi, Lead Management System in Ranchi, Lead Management Software Ranchi, Lead Tracking Software Ranchi, Customer Lead Management system in Jharkhand, CRM Lead Tracking System in Jharkhand', '<p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Managing leads efficiently is essential for turning inquiries into loyal customers. A well-structured lead management solution helps organizations capture, track, nurture, and convert prospects without missing valuable opportunities. As a trusted <strong>Lead Management Software Company in Ranchi, Jharkhand,</strong> Global Webify delivers intelligent solutions designed to simplify sales processes and improve conversion rates.</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Our <strong>Custom Lead Management System</strong> is tailored to meet the unique requirements of different industries. Whether handling hundreds of inquiries daily or managing a growing sales pipeline, a customized platform ensures every lead is organized, monitored, and assigned to the right team member. With automated workflows, real-time tracking, and detailed reporting, organizations can focus on building relationships while the system handles repetitive tasks.</span></p><h2><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Boost Sales Growth with a Smart Lead Management System in Ranchi</strong></span></h2><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">A powerful <strong>Lead Management System in Ranchi</strong> enables organizations to streamline their entire customer acquisition process. From capturing leads through websites, social media platforms, and marketing campaigns to assigning and tracking them throughout the sales cycle, every stage becomes more efficient.</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Our professional <strong>Lead Management Software Services</strong> help teams improve productivity, reduce response times, and maximize revenue opportunities. Advanced automation features ensure no prospect is overlooked while providing sales representatives with complete visibility into lead status and customer interactions.</span></p><h4><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Services Included</strong></span></h4><ul><li><p>Custom lead management software development</p></li><li><p>Lead capture and inquiry management</p></li><li><p>Sales pipeline tracking</p></li><li><p>Lead assignment automation</p></li><li><p>Follow-up reminder systems</p></li><li><p>CRM integration solutions</p></li><li><p>Reporting and analytics dashboards</p></li><li><p>Marketing campaign tracking</p></li><li><p>Mobile-friendly lead management tools</p></li><li><p>Cloud-based lead management solutions</p></li></ul><h3><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>What Is a Lead Management System and How Does It Work?</strong></span></h3><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">A lead management system is software designed to organize and manage potential customer information throughout the sales journey. It centralizes lead data and helps teams track interactions, monitor progress, and improve conversion rates.</span></p><h4><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Process</strong></span></h4><ol><li><p>Lead information is collected from multiple sources.</p></li><li><p>Leads are automatically categorized and assigned.</p></li><li><p>Sales representatives receive instant notifications.</p></li><li><p>Follow-up activities are scheduled and tracked.</p></li><li><p>Customer interactions are recorded in one platform.</p></li><li><p>Leads move through different sales stages.</p></li><li><p>Performance reports provide valuable business insights.</p></li><li><p>Converted leads become customers while nurturing continues for future opportunities.</p></li></ol><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">This structured process helps sales teams work more effectively while ensuring consistent communication with prospects.</span></p><h3><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Benefits of a Lead Management System</strong></span></h3><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Implementing a smart lead management solution offers several advantages for growing organizations.</span></p><ul><li><p>Faster response to customer inquiries</p></li><li><p>Improved lead tracking and visibility</p></li><li><p>Higher conversion rates</p></li><li><p>Better sales team productivity</p></li><li><p>Reduced manual data entry</p></li><li><p>Automated follow-up management</p></li><li><p>Enhanced customer engagement</p></li><li><p>Accurate sales forecasting</p></li><li><p>Centralized lead database</p></li><li><p>Detailed performance analytics</p></li><li><p>Better collaboration among teams</p></li><li><p>Increased return on marketing investments</p></li></ul><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">These benefits help organizations create a more organized sales process and achieve sustainable growth.</span></p><h3><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Why Choose Us as Your Lead Management Software Company in Ranchi</strong></span></h3><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Selecting the right software partner is crucial for long-term success. Our team focuses on developing scalable and user-friendly solutions that align with business objectives.</span></p><h4><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>What Makes Us Different?</strong></span></h4><ul><li><p>Customized software tailored to specific business needs</p></li><li><p>Easy-to-use and intuitive interface</p></li><li><p>Scalable solutions for growing organizations</p></li><li><p>Advanced automation capabilities</p></li><li><p>Secure data management practices</p></li><li><p>Real-time reporting and analytics</p></li><li><p>Seamless integration with existing tools</p></li><li><p>Dedicated technical support</p></li><li><p>Cost-effective development approach</p></li><li><p>Continuous system upgrades and maintenance</p></li></ul><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Global Webify combines technology expertise with industry knowledge to create lead management solutions that simplify operations and support business growth. Our focus on performance, automation, and user experience helps organizations manage prospects efficiently and convert more leads into long-term customers.</span></p>\n<!-- FAQ_DATA: [{"question":"What is Lead Management Software?","answer":"Lead Management Software is a powerful solution that helps businesses capture, organize, track, and manage customer inquiries from different sources. It allows teams to monitor lead status, automate follow-ups, and improve conversions through a structured sales process."},{"question":"Why does my business need Lead Management Software?","answer":"Lead Management Software helps businesses prevent lead loss, improve response time, track customer interactions, and manage sales pipelines efficiently. It ensures that every potential customer is followed up at the right time."},{"question":"Can I manage leads from multiple sources in one place?","answer":"Yes, our Lead Management Software allows businesses to manage leads collected from websites, inquiry forms, social media campaigns, advertisements, and other sources through a centralized dashboard."},{"question":"Is Global Webify Lead Management Software customizable?","answer":"Yes, Global Webify develops customized lead management solutions according to your business requirements, industry needs, sales process, and workflow."},{"question":"Can small and medium businesses use Lead Management Software?","answer":"Yes, Lead Management Software is suitable for startups, small businesses, and enterprises looking to organize leads, improve customer relationships, and increase business growth."}] -->', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552664730-d307ca884978?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80', 'crm', '2026-06-12 06:38:43', '2026-06-20 05:31:22', 1, 'Convert More Prospects with Ranchi''s Trusted Lead Management Software Company', 'Partner with a trusted Lead Management Software Company in Ranchi, Jharkhand, to automate lead tracking, streamline follow-ups, and increase conversions. Our intelligent software helps businesses manage prospects and accelerate sales growth.\n', 'image', '#062013', '#062013', '#0c3e25', NULL, NULL),
(91119, '/hotel-management-software', 'Hotel Management Software in Ranchi', 'Hotel Management Software in Ranchi, Hotel CRM System in Ranchi', 'Boost hotel operations with Hotel Management Software in Ranchi and Hotel CRM System in Ranchi, Jhrakhand by Global Webify. Streamline bookings, guest management, and customer relationships with ease. Contact us today for a customized solution!', 'Hotel Management Software in Ranchi, Hotel CRM System in Ranchi, Hotel Software Development Ranchi, Hotel Booking Management Software in Jharkhand, Hotel CRM Solutions Ranchi, Hotel Automation Software in Jharkhand', '<p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Managing a hotel requires seamless coordination between reservations, guest services, billing, housekeeping, and customer communication. A modern <strong>Hotel Management Software in Ranchi, Jharkhand,</strong> helps hotels, resorts, guest houses, and hospitality businesses automate daily operations while delivering exceptional guest experiences.</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">With advanced automation tools and centralized management, hospitality businesses can reduce manual work, improve operational efficiency, and maintain complete control over bookings, customer records, and revenue management. A reliable system enables staff to focus more on guest satisfaction rather than administrative tasks.</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Global Webify provides smart hospitality technology solutions designed to simplify hotel operations and improve business performance.</span></p><h3><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>What is a Hospitality and Hotel CRM?</strong></span></h3><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">A <strong>hospitality CRM solution</strong> is a specialized customer relationship management platform created for hotels and hospitality businesses. It helps manage guest interactions, booking histories, preferences, feedback, and communication from a single dashboard.</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">The system allows hotel owners and managers to:</span></p><ul><li><p>Store guest profiles and booking history</p></li><li><p>Manage inquiries and reservations efficiently</p></li><li><p>Track guest preferences for personalized services</p></li><li><p>Automate email and SMS communication</p></li><li><p>Improve customer retention and repeat bookings</p></li><li><p>Monitor hotel performance with detailed reports</p></li><li><p>Enhance guest engagement throughout their journey</p></li></ul><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">A hotel CRM combined with management software creates a complete ecosystem for handling operations and customer relationships effectively.</span></p><h3><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Benefits of Hotel Management Software</strong></span></h3><h4><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Simplified Reservation Management</strong></span></h4><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Manage direct bookings, online reservations, and walk-in guests through a centralized platform that reduces booking errors and overbooking risks.</span></p><h4><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Improved Operational Efficiency</strong></span></h4><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Automate routine tasks such as check-ins, check-outs, invoicing, and room allocation, allowing staff to work more productively.</span></p><h4><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Better Revenue Management</strong></span></h4><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Monitor room occupancy, pricing strategies, and revenue trends to maximize profitability and improve business planning.</span></p><h4><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Enhanced Guest Experience</strong></span></h4><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Access guest preferences and stay history to provide personalized services that increase customer satisfaction and loyalty.</span></p><h4><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Accurate Reporting &amp; Analytics</strong></span></h4><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Generate detailed reports on occupancy rates, bookings, revenue, customer behavior, and staff performance for informed decision-making.</span></p><h3><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Key Services Included</strong></span></h3><ul><li><p>Reservation Management</p></li><li><p>Front Desk Management</p></li><li><p>Housekeeping Tracking</p></li><li><p>Billing &amp; Invoicing</p></li><li><p>Multi-Property Management</p></li><li><p>Guest Database Management</p></li><li><p>Automated Notifications</p></li><li><p>Revenue Management</p></li><li><p>Analytics &amp; Reporting</p></li><li><p>Customer Feedback Tracking</p></li></ul><h2><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Boost Bookings &amp; Guest Satisfaction with a Smart Hotel CRM System in Ranchi</strong></span></h2><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Building strong relationships with guests is essential for long-term success in the hospitality industry. A powerful <strong>Hotel CRM System in Ranchi</strong> helps hotels engage customers more effectively, improve communication, and create personalized experiences that encourage repeat bookings.</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">A modern <strong>hospitality CRM solution</strong> centralizes guest information, automates communication, and helps hotel teams deliver superior service at every touchpoint.</span></p><h3><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Powerful Features of a Hotel CRM System</strong></span></h3><ul><li><p>Centralized guest profile management</p></li><li><p>Automated email and SMS campaigns</p></li><li><p>Booking inquiry tracking</p></li><li><p>Customer feedback collection</p></li><li><p>Lead and reservation management</p></li><li><p>Personalized guest communication</p></li><li><p>Loyalty program management</p></li><li><p>Task and follow-up automation</p></li><li><p>Real-time analytics and reporting</p></li><li><p>Multi-channel communication support</p></li></ul><h3><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Why Every Hotel Needs a CRM System</strong></span></h3><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Hotels that implement a CRM system gain significant advantages in customer engagement and operational efficiency.</span></p><h4><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Increased Guest Retention</strong></span></h4><ul><li><p>Maintain complete guest records</p></li><li><p>Deliver personalized experiences</p></li><li><p>Build stronger customer relationships</p></li><li><p>Encourage repeat visits</p></li></ul><h4><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Better Communication</strong></span></h4><ul><li><p>Automate booking confirmations</p></li><li><p>Send promotional offers instantly</p></li><li><p>Share important updates with guests</p></li><li><p>Improve response times</p></li></ul><h4><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Higher Booking Conversion</strong></span></h4><ul><li><p>Track inquiries efficiently</p></li><li><p>Follow up with potential guests</p></li><li><p>Reduce missed opportunities</p></li><li><p>Improve reservation management</p></li></ul><h4><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Enhanced Customer Satisfaction</strong></span></h4><ul><li><p>Understand guest preferences</p></li><li><p>Resolve issues faster</p></li><li><p>Collect valuable feedback</p></li><li><p>Deliver consistent service quality</p></li></ul><h4><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>Data-Driven Decisions</strong></span></h4><ul><li><p>Analyze customer behavior</p></li><li><p>Monitor booking trends</p></li><li><p>Measure campaign performance</p></li><li><p>Optimize hospitality strategies</p></li></ul><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Hotels, resorts, boutique properties, and guest houses can significantly improve operational efficiency and customer satisfaction by implementing an advanced CRM and hotel management platform. The right technology helps streamline workflows, strengthen guest relationships, and create memorable hospitality experiences that drive long-term business growth.</span></p>\n<!-- FAQ_DATA: [{"question":"What is Hotel Management Software?","answer":"Hotel Management Software is a digital solution that helps hotels, resorts, and hospitality businesses manage daily operations such as room bookings, guest records, check-ins, billing, payments, housekeeping, and reports from a single platform. Global Webify provides customized hotel software solutions to simplify hotel operations and improve efficiency."},{"question":"Why does my hotel need Hotel Management Software?","answer":"Hotel Management Software helps reduce manual work, avoid booking errors, improve guest experience, and manage hotel operations efficiently. It allows hotel owners and staff to track reservations, rooms, payments, and business performance in real time."},{"question":"Can Global Webify develop customized Hotel Management Software?","answer":"Yes, Global Webify provides customized Hotel Management Software Development according to your hotel’s specific requirements. We create scalable solutions for hotels, resorts, guest houses, and hospitality businesses."},{"question":"Is Hotel Management Software suitable for small hotels?","answer":"Yes, Hotel Management Software is suitable for small, medium, and large hotels. It helps small hotels automate daily tasks, manage bookings easily, and improve customer service without complicated processes."},{"question":"Can I manage multiple hotel branches with this software?","answer":"Yes, customized hotel management software can support multi-property or multi-branch management. Hotel owners can manage rooms, staff, bookings, and reports from a centralized dashboard."},{"question":"Does Hotel Management Software help increase hotel revenue?","answer":"Yes, hotel software helps improve revenue by reducing booking mistakes, managing room availability, tracking performance reports, and enabling better decision-making through accurate business insights."}] -->', 'https://images.unsplash.c