(30001, 'homepageHeroTexts', '["Up to 67% of Customers Judge Your Business Online First","Manage Smarter. Sell Faster. Grow Stronger — With ERP & CRM.","If You’re Not on Page One, You’re Losing Customers.","Your Website Should Win Customers — Not Repel Them.","Turn Every Lead Into a Loyal Customer With the Right CRM.","Rank Higher. Get Found. Grow Consistently.","Turn Every Visitor Into a Potential Customer through your website","If You Can’t Track It, You Can’t Scale It — ERP & CRM Make It Possible.","Your Customers Are Searching — Are They Finding You or Your Competitors?","वेबसाइट नहीं, तो विश्वास भी नहीं।","बिखरा हुआ बिज़नेस नहीं — पूरी तरह नियंत्रित और संगठित।","वेबसाइट जो ब्रांड भी बनाए, बिज़नेस भी बढ़ाए।","गूगल पर दिखेंगे तभी ग्राहक मिलेंगे।","सर्च में पीछे, तो बिज़नेस में पीछे।","हर लीड को ग्राहक और हर ग्राहक को दोबारा ग्राहक बनाइए।"]'),
